and a few more...

WHOLESALE orders are welcome, please contact me for more info

name: 'Selene' Charm Bracelet in Copper and Amethyst
description:
Made up of tiny copper pine cone charms, copper droplets, freshwater pearls, vintage bead caps and glass beads in milk white, blueberry purple and amethyst. Gathered on an antiqued copper chain and finished with a simple toggle clasp

◢◢◢ SIZE and DETAILS ◣◣◣

7.5 inches around. Fits an adult wrist 
I can shorten the chain for you if desired

Chain and Toggle Clasp fastenings are high quality copper findings, very strong and beautiful. The warm copper charms and jewel tone beads catch and reflect light, making this bracelet a delight to wear in any season for any occasion.

◢◢◢ SHIPPING ◣◣◣

♥ Gift wrapped in a cute little decorated handmade box tied with a satin ribbon & Ginger Kelly tag.

♥ Shipped in a secure bubble wrap mailer. Please see my shop policies for further shipping info & estimated shipping times

name: Custom Made Fox, Felt Woodland Critter
description:
Handmade felt fox. Made to order with your choice of color, fabric pattern and with tiny details unique to each individual. Hand stitched and decorated with a vintage crochet or lace ruff and tiny buttons.

◢◢◢ SIZE and DETAILS ◣◣◣

A variety of colors are available, with white accents on the feet, ears and eye patches... or I can use a fabric from my collection ~ I will have some more pics soon to show the fabrics I have in stock. 
I can also add whiskers, eyelashes, eyes of blue, green, brown or black. More pics to see soon! 

Approx 6.5 inches tall. One of a Kind. Pocket size toy or bookshelf pet.


◢◢◢ MADE FROM ◣◣◣

All my little critters are made from a beautiful soft wool blend felt and 100% cotton quilting fabric body. They have black or color safety eyes, a hand stitched embroidered nose and are stuffed with polyfill and felt scraps. A pretty vintage crochet or lace trim is used for the ruff collar. 


◢◢◢ SHIPPING ◣◣◣

Safely shipped to you tucked inside a handmade calico sleeping bag, tied with ribbon & a Thistle and Fox label. Each little felt creature arrives with a name card which tells a little story of how they came to be. 


◢◢◢ OTHER INFO ◣◣◣

As this item is made to order please allow 7-14 days for your fox to be lovingly handcrafted. I will notify via Etsy shipping notification when your fox is on its way to you.


Pattern is from the lovely Shelly of Gingermelon.etsy.com

If you are purchasing for a child please use parental judgement. This fox has some small bits and is at his best when handled gently. 


Any questions, please contact me
